Assignment: Write a detailed prompt for security testing of a credit card transaction

ICED TO

[Role] As a Manual Security Tester, 
[Instruction] 
- Write detailed secuity testing testcases for a credit card transaction
- Output should cover positive, negative and many edge cases 

[Context] Credit card transactions are used by the users to do online payments
[Examples] example of a testcase is 
TC001 : Testcase Title
Testcase Description
Test Data
Expected Output

[Desired Output] 
- Output should cover any vulnerabilities
- Output should have frauding scenarios
- Output format should match with the example provided above
- Each testcase should be from user's perspective

[Tone] All test cases should be maintained in a Professional Tone